data.description: Nestled in the charming city of McDonough, Georgia, this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom traditional home invites you to experience the perfect blend of classic style and contemporary convenience. This home offers the tranquility of suburban living while being just a short drive away from local amenities, schools, and parks. The heart of the home is a spacious eat-in kitchen, and the convenience of a laundry room on the main level. The large master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a cozy sitting area. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home. Schedule a private tour today and experience the timeless allure of this McDonough gem.
